@FelloWay.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7086

### LinkedIn BFF — start sign-in (browser/mobile opens this URL; AddLinkedIn Challenge)
GET {{FelloWay.Api_HostAddress}}/auth/linkedin/login?returnUrl=https://localhost:7357&platform=web

### LinkedIn BFF — mobile ticket exchange (after com.felloway.app://auth/callback?ticket=...)
POST {{FelloWay.Api_HostAddress}}/auth/linkedin/mobile/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ticket": "replace-with-ticket-from-redirect"
}

### Session probe (cookie or bearer)
GET {{FelloWay.Api_HostAddress}}/auth/session

### Production sign-in: use LinkedIn BFF (not dev authorization codes on deployed API)
# GET {{FelloWay.Api_HostAddress}}/auth/linkedin/login?returnUrl=https://localhost:7357&platform=web

### Run API: dotnet run --project backend/src/FelloWay.Api --launch-profile https
